attempts.sparql_query: PREFIX atm: <https://data.nasa.gov/ontologies/atmonto/ATM#> PREFIX eqp: <https://data.nasa.gov/ontologies/atmonto/equipment#> SELECT?aircraftModel WHERE { atm:ASA14-201407150005 atm:aircraftFlown?aircraft.?aircraft eqp:hasAircraftModel?aircraftModel. }
attempts.query_explanation: This SPARQL query retrieves the aircraft model for flight ASA14 by first identifying the aircraft flown by ASA14 and then retrieving its aircraft model.
